Package: pairwiseAlignment
Title: Perform pairwise sequence alignments
Description: Solves (Needleman-Wunsch) global alignment, (Smith-Waterman) local
	alignment, and (ends-free) overlap alignment problems.
biocViews: Alignment, SequenceMatching, Sequencing, Genetics
URL: https://bioconductor.org/packages/pairwiseAlignment
BugReports: https://github.com/Bioconductor/pairwiseAlignment/issues
Version: 0.0.0
License: Artistic-2.0
Encoding: UTF-8
